show.description: Dinesh hides his true identity from his wife, Vartika, initially investing secretly in her fashion start-up out of genuine love. Their relationship faces severe turmoil when suspicions of infidelity and deception arise, primarily involving Monty, who becomes entangled in their lives, further complicating matters.
